---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const city = "Salt Lake City";
const tdsLevel = "350-500 ppm";
---

<Layout
  title="Water Filtration Salt Lake City - Blue Logic Water"
  description="Professional reverse osmosis systems for Salt Lake City homes. Combat Utah's hard water with commercial-grade filtration at half the cost."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Water Purification for {city}</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Professional RO systems designed for Utah's unique water challenges
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="water-quality">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Understanding {city}'s Water</h2>

      <div class="water-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{tdsLevel}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Total Dissolved Solids (TDS)</div>
          <p>
            Salt Lake City water typically contains high mineral content due to
            mountain runoff and geological factors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">Very Hard</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Water Hardness Rating</div>
          <p>
            Utah consistently ranks among the hardest water states in the
            nation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="water-info">
        <h3>What's in Your Water?</h3>
        <p>
          Salt Lake City's water supply comes from mountain watersheds and
          underground sources. While generally safe to drink, it contains high
          levels of:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Calcium and Magnesium:</strong> The minerals that make water "hard"
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Chlorine:</strong> Added for disinfection, can affect taste
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Trace minerals:</strong> Iron, manganese, and other naturally
            occurring elements
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Potential contaminants:</strong> Varying levels of PFAS, lead
            from old pipes, and agricultural runoff
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-ro">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Reverse Osmosis for Utah Homes?</h2>

      <div class="reason-grid">
        <div class="reason-card">
          <h3>Eliminates Hard Water</h3>
          <p>
            RO removes 99%+ of dissolved minerals, eliminating scale buildup on
            fixtures, appliances, and plumbing. No more spotty dishes or clogged
            showerheads.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-card">
          <h3>Removes Contaminants</h3>
          <p>
            Beyond minerals, RO removes chlorine, PFAS, heavy metals, and other
            potential contaminants that simple filters can't touch.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-card">
          <h3>Better for Your Health</h3>
          <p>
            Pure water means fewer skin irritations, better hydration, and peace
            of mind knowing what's NOT in your water.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-card">
          <h3>Protects Your Home</h3>
          <p>
            Prevent costly damage to water heaters, dishwashers, and plumbing
            systems caused by mineral buildup.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="local-service">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Local Service for Local Challenges</h2>
      <p class="service-text">
        We live and work in the Wasatch Front. We understand Utah's water
        because it's our water too. Every Blue Logic system is optimized for the
        specific challenges of Salt Lake Valley water quality.
      </p>

      <div class="service-areas">
        <h3>Serving the Entire Wasatch Front</h3>
        <div class="area-grid">
          <span>Salt Lake City</span>
          <span>Park City</span>
          <span>Draper</span>
          <span>Sandy</span>
          <span>Cottonwood Heights</span>
          <span>Holladay</span>
          <span>Murray</span>
          <span>Millcreek</span>
          <span>South Jordan</span>
          <span>West Jordan</span>
          <span>Taylorsville</span>
          <span>West Valley City</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="local-proof">
    <div class="container center">
      <h2>Trusted by 500+ Wasatch Front Families</h2>
      <p>
        From downtown Salt Lake to the foothills, local families trust Blue
        Logic for professional water purification at a fair price.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container center">
      <h2>Get Your Free {city} Water Quality Assessment</h2>
      <p>See exactly what's in your water and how we can help</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="cta-button">Schedule Free Audit</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      oklch(0.95 0.01 90) 0%,
      oklch(0.85 0.05 220) 100%
    );
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .container.center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .water-quality {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .water-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: oklch(0.2 0.02 270);
  }

  .stat-card p {
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .water-info {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .water-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .water-info p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .water-info ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .water-info li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(0.9 0.01 90);
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .water-info li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .why-ro {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
  }

  .reason-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .reason-card {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .reason-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
  }

  .reason-card p {
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .local-service {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .service-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
  }

  .service-areas {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .service-areas h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .area-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .area-grid span {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    color: oklch(0.3 0.02 270);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .local-proof {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
  }

  .local-proof p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .water-stats,
    .reason-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .area-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
